data.description: Location! Location! Location! This 2/2 condo is located in the beautiful community of The Estuary. It's a first floor, lakeview, corner unit which means - no stairs and extra windows!! This condo is just waiting for you to come along and add your personal taste and style! It's a blank slate. The kitchen is large enough for a small table and open to the combined dining/living area. Master bedroom can accommodate a king sized bed and there's a large walk-in closet. Extra storage available in the closet on the screened patio. Washer and dryer are in unit and almost new! This condo can be rented immediately for a min of 3 months, twice per year. The Estuary is a beautiful community located on the St. Lucie River near numerous shopping and dining possibilities.
